The paper discusses the use of machine learning models for automatic genre classification of newspaper articles, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the importance of model transparency and responsible usage, which could fall under the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
